
üîß Step 1: Update WSL Ubuntu
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y
üîß Step 2: Install Java (Hadoop needs Java 8/11)
sudo apt install openjdk-11-jdk -y
Check version:

java -version
üîß Step 3: Create Hadoop User (optional but recommended)
sudo adduser hadoop
sudo usermod -aG sudo hadoop
su - hadoop
üîß Step 4: Download Hadoop
wget https://downloads.apache.org/hadoop/common/hadoop-3.3.6/hadoop-3.3.6.tar.gz
Extract:

tar -xvzf hadoop-3.3.6.tar.gz
Move Hadoop:

sudo mv hadoop-3.3.6 /usr/local/hadoop
üîß Step 5: Set Environment Variables
Open .bashrc:

nano ~/.bashrc
Add these lines at the bottom:

export HADOOP_HOME=/usr/local/hadoop
export HADOOP_INSTALL=$HADOOP_HOME
export HADOOP_MAPRED_HOME=$HADOOP_HOME
export HADOOP_COMMON_HOME=$HADOOP_HOME
export HADOOP_HDFS_HOME=$HADOOP_HOME
export YARN_HOME=$HADOOP_HOME
export HADOOP_COMMON_LIB_NATIVE_DIR=$HADOOP_HOME/lib/native
export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-11-openjdk-amd64
export PATH=$PATH:$HADOOP_HOME/bin:$HADOOP_HOME/sbin
Reload:

source ~/.bashrc
üîß Step 6: Configure Hadoop Files
‚úî Edit hadoop-env.sh
nano /usr/local/hadoop/etc/hadoop/hadoop-env.sh
Add:

export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-11-openjdk-amd64
‚úî Edit core-site.xml
nano /usr/local/hadoop/etc/hadoop/core-site.xml
Add inside <configuration>:

<property>
  <name>fs.defaultFS</name>
  <value>hdfs://localhost:9000</value>
</property>
‚úî Edit hdfs-site.xml
nano /usr/local/hadoop/etc/hadoop/hdfs-site.xml
Add:

<property>
  <name>dfs.replication</name>
  <value>1</value>
</property>

<property>
  <name>dfs.namenode.name.dir</name>
  <value>file:///usr/local/hadoop/hadoop_data/hdfs/namenode</value>
</property>

<property>
  <name>dfs.datanode.data.dir</name>
  <value>file:///usr/local/hadoop/hadoop_data/hdfs/datanode</value>
</property>
üîê Step 7: Enable SSH (Hadoop requires SSH)
Install SSH:

sudo apt install openssh-server -y
Generate key:

ssh-keygen -t rsa
cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
chmod 600 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
Test:

ssh localhost
If you get a prompt ‚Üí type yes.

üîß Step 8: Format the Namenode
hdfs namenode -format
